edibles-fabric.duskconfig.title: Edibles Config
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_maxItemUs: The maximum amount of an item a player can eat before receiving the weakness effect. A value of -1 disables this feature.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.maxItemUsesPer: Max Item Uses Per Day Single Item
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_maxItemUs: The maximum of the total amount of items a player can eat before receiving the weakness effect. A value of -1 disables this feature.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.maxItemUsesPer: Max Item Uses Per Day Total
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_weaknessD: The duration of the weakness effect in seconds when eating too much of an item.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_glowEntit: When eating glowstone, the duration in seconds of how long entities around should be glowing with an outline. A value of 0 disables the item use.
For the glow effect, the radius in blocks around the player of entities affected.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.glowEntitiesAr: Glow Entities Around Affected Radius Blocks
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC__cooldown: The time in miliseconds of cooldown in between uses of eating an edible.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_blazePowd: After eating blaze powder, the duration in seconds of the strength effect the player receives. A value of 0 disables the item use.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_magmaCrea: After eating magma cream, the duration in seconds of the fire resistance effect the player receives. A value of 0 disables the item use.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.magmaCreamFire: Magma Cream Fire Resistance Duration Seconds
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_sugarSpee: After eating some sugar, the duration in seconds of the speed effect the player receives. A value of 0 disables the item use.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_ghastTear: After eating a ghast tear, the duration in seconds of the regeneration effect the player receives. A value of 0 disables the item use.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_phantomMe: After eating some phantom membrane, the duration in seconds of the slow falling effect the player receives. A value of 0 disables the item use.
edibles-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_rabbitsFo: After eating a rabbit's foot, the duration in seconds of the jump boost effect the player receives. A value of 0 disables the item use.
